    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A shaman surrounds herself with the spirit of battle. Allies within 30 feet of the shaman (including the shaman) receive a +1 morale bonus on attack rolls and weapon damage rolls.</p>\n<p>At 8th level and 16th level, these bonuses increase by 1.</p>\n<p>The shaman can use this ability for a number of rounds per day equal to 3 + her Charisma modifier. These rounds do not need to be consecutive.</p>"
